desc_short	-----								Blasters of the Universe is the first of its kind, bringing the “shmup” genre into VR. Intense gameplay is heavily reliant on physical movement, requiring the player to duck, dodge, twist, turn, and maneuver their way through waves of enemies and hundreds of bullets in a neon-tech inspired virtual world.							
